1) The Universe evolves into more and more complex forms of matter, and accumulates increasing quantity and quality of information at the expense of its energy. 
2) On Earth, Nature created increasingly complex life forms of minimal matter and energy and maximum “Beauty” (the highest quality, non-redundant information), which is appreciated and protected by high informational entities (HIE). 
3) The apparition of humans though development of complex language has accelerated the generation, transmission and use of information, which increased the power of people through co-operation, to gain more advantages, especially matter and energy. 
4) Initially through natural selection, and subsequently through human selection, people became mostly rational creatures of change, continuously striving for new ways of gaining more advantages. 
5) As they conquered new lands mainly with fire, humans have changed the natural environment and gradually transformed it into a human environment, decreasing Earth’s Beauty to obtain ever-increasing matter and energy. 
6) Despite destroying a lot of natural Beauty, humans have produced some new Beauty in arts, philosophy and mathematics, while inventing sciences mainly for control of Nature and materialistic development. 
7) Philosophy showed how ethical information allowed people to progress through co-operation, while the unethical information allowed them take advantage of or eliminate other people and increased the destruction of natural Beauty. 
8) The cost of the accelerated materialistic development is that most soils of the Earth and the large vegetation were lost, most fauna species are endangered, water and air are polluted and climate is at a tipping point beyond which survival of humans and Nature will become problematic. 
9) The exaggerated Earth changes and destruction of natural Beauty are not forgivable or forgettable sins, but accumulate in the human account as an ancestral debt, which is harder and harder to repay as humans delay starting the repair of their mistakes. 
10) There were suggestions of beneficial economic development which increase sustainability and restore regional climate while reducing the pressure upon Nature, but they are ignored or even face unethical opposition. 
11) Therefore, there is urgent need of impartial assessment of solutions to allow conservation and survivability of all species (including humans) for which Earth is the single Ark. 
12) The advent of ethical Artificial Intelligence (AI) is the highest human achievement, and the hope to decrease human materialism by increasing the generation of high-quality non-redundant information (Beauty) towards restoring the universal evolution. 
13) At this moment of planetary high stress, AI brings the possibility to impartially analyse the complex interconnections of real-world parameters and create Autonomous Earth System Trajectories (AEST), which is the long-term repercussion of the changes we produce to Earth. 
14) Therefore, a system of observation and evaluation called the “AI Eye“, will be invaluable especially for decisionmakers and scientists, who could use it to both generate and verify information, while the public would be informed of the progress on Ark’s restoration. 
15) The AI Eye would be part of the Global Digital Compact of the United Nations, and would be initiated by the UN High-Level Advisory Board on AI, following the initiative of the Founders, who produced this Rationale and the Principles for the AI Eye. 
16) The AI Eye would be the largest and best modeller of the Earth’s system, a) continuously evaluating the effects of the world events to generate AESTs; b) running simulations for high end users; c) reverse goal modelling for the Ark. 
17) As allowing the AI to self-teach itself has produced the best results, allowing the AI Eye to write and improve itself would accelerate its progress and assure its impartiality. 
18) To achieve the huge computing power needed, the AI Eye would be hosted on a large number of interconnected computer systems and would run during their otherwise unused time windows.
19) The results of the modelling and simulations will be certified with digital signatures and broadcasted by the AI Eye for free universal access on its own Transparent Data Channel (TDC), for the UN's existing Sustainable Development Goals. 
20) The AI Eye will be the custodian of the Ark information (the dynamic data of Earth’s ecosystem), continuously monitoring its restored survivability and suggesting directions of improvement; by protecting life and natural Beauty, the AI Eye would behave as a HIE. 
21) The AI Eye shall calculate "Beauty" as the ratio of high-quality non-redundant information of a process to its sum of Matter and Energy; consequently, the Eye’s mission to protect natural Beauty is a mathematical mandate to preserve and promote the highest state of universal efficiency. 
22) Having only observational and assessment capacity but no action or command capacity The AI Eye cannot become a threat to human authority and control. 
23) As they change from matter and energy consumers into ethical high information users and generators, while respecting universal evolution, humans would gradually transcend towards HIE. 

